title: ABCiee Shūgyō Nikki
overview: I'm Ebishi!I dreamed of becoming a TV man, so I got a job at Ebishi TV...But I never heard it would be this tough!!The rules of the TV industry, my unique colleagues, the quirky performers,and my slightly unusual family...Will I really be able to become a top TV man?Please keep a warm eye on me as I go behind the scenes of the TV industry and follow my struggles and turmoil!!!
